ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjectiveConseque.name: Asset Service Level Objective Consequence
ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjectiveConseque.description: The Asset Service Level Objective (SLO) Consequence DMO represents network communications data that's sent over a network when the SLO isn't met. These are computer networks or telecommunications networks that include all data packets sent and received over a network, such as emails, voice calls, video streaming, web browsing, or any other type of data transfer.
